mco.account.privacy.information:
Chak' jayibuk mantaletik sventa skolta ta stuk'ulanel ololetik xchi'uk smukulalik li Mojang-e; ja' yu'un, chch'un smantal Ley ta Stuk'ulanel Smukulalik Ololetik ta Internet (COPPA ta inkles k'op) xchi'uk Komon Mantalal ta Stuk'ulanel Alelal (RGPD ta kaxlan k'op).

mco.account.privacyinfo:
Chak' jayibuk mantaletik sventa skolta ta stuk'ulanel ololetik xchi'uk smukulalik li Mojang-e k'alal chch'un smantal Ley ta Stuk'ulanel Smukulalik Ololetik ta Internet (COPPA ta inkles k'op) xchi'uk Komon Mantalal ta Stuk'ulanel Alelal (RGPD ta kaxlan k'op).

Sk'an nan chak'bot ak'el li atot ame'e ta ba'i sventa xu' xasa' li akuentae yu'un Realms.

Mi oy to apoko' kuentae yu'un Minecraft (sventa chalikes sesion sk'an chatunes jun biilal jtunesvanej, mu'yuk jun koreo), sk'an chavuy li akuentae ta jun kuenta yu'un Mojang sventa chavich' Realms.

Minecratf ch'abal xa smemoria.

Li' k'ot nan ta pasele yu'un ch'ay xa'i li tajimole o yu'un mu ak'batik xe'el avil li arkumentoetike ta JVM yu'un ts'akel ta jimvanej.

Sventa mu chyaj li tajimole, la smakoj sba. La jk'ankutik jkolkutik li k'anbil avile sventa chasut ta ba'yel menu xchi'uk chasut ta tajimol, pe mu abtejem nan li'e.

Cha'likeso li tajimole mi chavil nixtok li mantal li'e, avokoluk.

telemetry.event.advancement_made.descrip: Mi chka'ikutik smelol li k'usi chk'ot ta pasel k'alal chpasat jun porokresoe, ja' tskoltaunkutik ta ya'iel xchi'uk slekubtasel li sporokresion tajimole.

telemetry.event.game_load_times.descript: Xu' skoltaunkutik ta yilel bu sk'an lekubtaseletik ta rentimiento likel li tajimoltik li'e k'alal chat li sk'ak'alil ak'eletike.
telemetry.event.game_load_times.title: Sk'ak'alil svinajesel tajimol
telemetry.event.performance_metrics.desc:
Mi jna'kutik li analis rentimientoe yu'un Minecraft ta tsobol ja' tskoltaunkutik ta slekubtasel li tajimole sventa li smas-toyol-atolalik k'aneletik xchi'uk operasional sistemaetik. 
Tskap sba li yach'ubtasel tajimole sventa jko'oltaskutik li analisis rentimientoe xchi'uk ach' ach'ubtaseletik yu'un Minecraft.
telemetry.event.world_load_times.descrip: Sk'an jna'kutik k'u yepal sk'ak'alil chjok'tsaj sventa cha-och ta jun balumil xchi'uk k'uxi le'e sjel sba ta patil. Jech k'ucha'al, k'alal jkapkutik ach' karakteristikaetik o jpaskutik muk'ta jeleletik ta teknika, sk'an jk'elkutik k'usi majel oy ta sk'ak'alil vinajeseletik.
telemetry.event.world_load_times.title: Sk'ak'alil svinajelal balumil
telemetry.event.world_loaded.description:
Mi jna'kutik k'uxi chtajinik Minecraft li jtajimoletike (k'usi manera tajimol, kiliente o jelel servilor xchi'uk yach'ubtasel tajimol tstunesik le'ike) ja' tskoltaunkutik ta slekubtasel li aspektoetike ti mas chak'ik ta venta li jtajimoletike.
Li tajimoltike ''vinajesbil balumil'' ja' ts'akal ta tajimoltik ''yalesbil balumil'' sventa chat k'u yepal sk'ak'alil jalijem li sesion tajimole.
telemetry.event.world_loaded.title: Vinajesbil balumil
telemetry.event.world_unloaded.descripti:
Ts'akal ta tajimoltik ''vinajesbil balumil'' li tajimoltik li'e sventa chat k'u yepal jalijem li sesion tajimole.
Li jalijele (ta sekuntoetik xchi'uk sikloetik) ja' chp'isat k'alal chlaj jun sesion tajimol (k'alal chalok' ta ba'yel menu o k'alal chach'ak aba ta jun servilor).
telemetry.event.world_unloaded.title: Yalesbil balumil
